A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu nke Western Cape Provincial na ntuli aka 2009
Ọ malitere ọrụ na 6 Mee na afọ 2009.

A họpụtara Beerwinkel ọzọ maka oge nke abụọ dị ka onye omeiwu mpaghara na ntuli aka mpaghara nke afọ 2014. Ọ hapụrụ ndị omeiwu mpaghara na 7 Mee na afọ 2019, ebe ọ na-etinyeghị ya na ndepụta ANC maka ntuli aka mpaghara nke afọ ahụ.
